<h3>Configuration Examples</h3>

<div class="aui-message info">
    <p><strong>Repository Level:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Enable hook for specific repositories that deploy to production</li>
        <li>Customize patterns for repository-specific config files</li>
        <li>Set to warning mode for development repositories</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="aui-message info">
    <p><strong>Project Level:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Enable hook for all repositories in a project</li>
        <li>Set standard patterns across the entire project</li>
